    "created_at": "2015-09-14T09:11:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-14T09:11:24Z",
    "body": "The Electron used by Atom is a bit old for now, the next release of Atom will include Electron v0.29.x, and  there is also a PR(https://github.com/atom/atom/pull/8779) to update Electron to the latest one.\n\nConsidering G-Sync is relatively new, this is very likely to have been fixed by recent Chrome versions (e.g. recent Electron versions), so I'm closing this issue in Electron, but if the problem still exists after https://github.com/atom/atom/pull/8779 gets merged, I'll reopen the issue here.\n"
