    "updated_at": "2016-03-31T17:50:18Z",
    "body": "I also just tried out the [quick start app](https://github.com/atom/electron-quick-start) and updated package.json to reference 0.37.3 instead, and I'm seeing the exact same problem there.\n\nAt this point, I think it is safe to say that the latest electron hasn't fixed this problem, so this issue should be re-opened!\n"
